Date: Thu, 11 Mar 2021 23:38:35 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 08/14] winex11.drv: Use XPresentPixmap instead of XCopyArea
 when available.

Wine-Bug: https://bugs.winehq.org/show_bug.cgi?id=45277
CW-Bug-Id: 16608
---
